						Machine->Inv - filter items leaving the machine into the adjacent inventory
						Both - filter both directions
						'''
					NewString:
						'''
						Which direction the filter applies to
						Inv->Machine - filter items entering the machine from the adjacent inventory
						Machine->Inv - filter items leaving the machine into the adjacent inventory
						Both - filter both directions
						'''
				}

				2: {
					OldString:
						'''
						Behaviour for the direction the filter doesn't apply to
						Block - no flow in that direction
						Filter - apply the filter in that direction too
						Free - pass everything through unchecked
						'''
